{"tid":1550462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依家最有用既方法係麻包袋","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T10:53:39.000Z","uid":4191,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c2177a49e46c4b2d3f9848e2c684bdfafbec20eb","tid":1550462,"uid":4191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"發夢有人同我講：<br />\n<br />\n話依家做乜都無用，唯一可以做就係對休班狗落手<br />\n<br />\n組織幾個識既朋友做民間小隊，揀落單既，只要發生左頭幾單，就會愈來愈多做做<br />\n<br />\n只有令狗隻失去理智，先會有更多核彈出黎<br />\n<br />\n唔好再同我講咩會失去民意，班狗都無底線地無恥，我地仲要set 條底線比自己？<br />\n<br />\n利申多次先，尋晚發夢既野，現實唔好做，太危險了"},{"pid":"bdd5aa4f6467e1e8b8b9dfbd9c23796a81d7c68f","tid":1550462,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:10:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=3f0533ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"1fa6ac3c5614c4dac5a59e8d3383d7dd5d36d240","tid":1550462,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67e6e99eaef408d662075a83bf9b7d5166fd9f71","tid":1550462,"uid":74896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"日經"},{"pid":"c036e18224aab0ef38cc034f7d06f8a3fa270cb1","tid":1550462,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2